{
  "stem": "23131.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What about his dogs?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the first slaughter, May the 8th, 1942, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they then went, and they placed us already in a closed ghetto-- in a wired ghetto, in a closed ghetto, with five, six families in a house.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next morning we had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what did we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to clean up the-- the mess from the burning buildings, the bricks, to put it on such a, you know-- I forgot whatever you call this.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not wagons.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to carry it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't wheel it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Polish, it's [NON-ENGLISH], but in English, I don't know how to say it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you used to put on plenty of the-- from the house, I just said it-- the-- the bricks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you had to take this away from this place, and place it in a place where a truck came-- a German truck came.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they used to take it away and throw it away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to clean out the spaces where the buildings were completely clean, like never nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Sunday, here was this Werner, used to-- Winnisch, Winnisch was one of-- of the commanders in the Gebietskommissar.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Windisch, Windisch.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Sunday after breakfast, after all the luxury that he had-- the-- the bacon with-- with all the goodies-- he used to let the dogs down, feed them, too, with a very good breakfast-- much better than the people that had in the ghettos-- and then let them jump on the people.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let them free, and jump on the people that worked across the Gebietskommissar by cleaning up the-- there was plenty of times that they tear a person in-- in pieces.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
